    dc:description "Figures 1 - 4. Loxocera (Loxocera) chikuni sp. nov., holotype, male 1 habitus, lateral 2 head, dorsal 3 left antenna, dorsal 4 same, lateral. Scale bars: 3 mm (1); 0.5 mm (2); 1 mm (3, 4)." ;
